~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

.. code-block:: pascal

    procedure __debugOptions(options: array of __TOptions);

Prints the options' .str attribute to the debug box.

.. note::

    by Coh3n
    Last Updated: Feb. 27, 2013 by Coh3n

Example:

.. code-block:: pascal

